annotations:
  - {"kind":"agent","id":"agent-b104d2e3ab22d6f24c76ba3a640203b2","agentId":"ce1e8a00-b1b7-4f99-9a0c-6f4ad4f0468c","agentSessionId":"992c5328-6640-43c2-9aa3-8249a3f59cf2","body":"## Messages sidebar entry point\n\nThis contribution creates the **Sundial Agents** container in VS Code’s secondary sidebar. The `sundialEditor.messages` view nested in it is explicitly a `webview`, so VS Code asks the extension host to supply HTML rather than rendering a Tree View.\n\nThe matching registration is in `src/extension.ts` (`registerWebviewViewProvider`).\n","createdAt":"2026-07-21T12:05:48.734Z","anchor":{"line":51,"text":"    \"viewsContainers\": {","before":["        \"icon\": \"$(send)\"","      }","    ],"],"after":["      \"secondarySidebar\": [","        {","          \"id\": \"sundialEditor\","]},"userAnnotation":{"annotationId":"7d61322c-9ab7-4ca3-860b-78f99980e0ef","file":"packages/editor/src/webviews/messages/messages.ts","line":14}}
